---
// Wichtige Notfall-Kategorien als Card-Übersicht
---

<section class="bg-base-100 py-16 md:py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <span class="text-primary mb-4 block text-sm font-bold tracking-wider uppercase">
        Häufige Notfälle
      </span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">Wann Sie sofort handeln müssen</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/80 mx-auto mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg">
        Diese Situationen erfordern sofortige tierärztliche Hilfe. Zögern Sie nicht, uns zu
        kontaktieren.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Vergiftungen -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-error/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-error h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Vergiftungen</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Schokolade, Weintrauben, Zwiebeln</li>
            <li>• Giftpflanzen (Lilien, Efeu)</li>
            <li>• Rattengift oder Medikamente</li>
            <li>• Frostschutzmittel</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-warning text-warning mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Sofort anrufen! Nicht abwarten!</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Atemnot -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-error/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-error h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Atemnot</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Röcheln oder Pfeifen beim Atmen</li>
            <li>• Blaue Zunge/Zahnfleisch</li>
            <li>• Starkes Hecheln ohne Anstrengung</li>
            <li>• Panik, Unruhe</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-error text-error mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Lebensbedrohlich! Sofort handeln!</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Unfälle & Verletzungen -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-warning/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-warning h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Unfälle & Verletzungen</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Verkehrsunfälle</li>
            <li>• Starke Blutungen</li>
            <li>• Knochenbrüche</li>
            <li>• Bisswunden</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-info text-info mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Tier ruhig halten, Transport vorsichtig</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Magendrehung -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-error/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-error h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Magendrehung</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Aufgeblähter, harter Bauch</li>
            <li>• Würgen ohne Erbrechen</li>
            <li>• Unruhe, Hecheln</li>
            <li>• Schwäche, Kollaps</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-error text-error mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Absolute Dringlichkeit! Minuten entscheiden!</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Krampfanfälle -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-warning/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-warning h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Krampfanfälle</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Unkontrollierte Zuckungen</li>
            <li>• Bewusstlosigkeit</li>
            <li>• Speichelfluss, Einnässen</li>
            <li>• Dauer über 5 Minuten</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-warning text-warning mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Tier sichern, Zeit stoppen, danach Tierarzt</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Hitzschlag -->
      <div class="card bg-base-200/60 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="bg-error/10 mb-4 flex h-16 w-16 items-center justify-center rounded-full">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="text-error h-8 w-8"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M12 3v1m0 16v1m9-9h-1M4 12H3m15.364 6.364l-.707-.707M6.343 6.343l-.707-.707m12.728 0l-.707.707M6.343 17.657l-.707.707M16 12a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Hitzschlag</h3>
          <ul class="text-base-content/80 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• Starkes Hecheln, rote Zunge</li>
            <li>• Erbrechen, Durchfall</li>
            <li>• Taumeln, Bewusstlosigkeit</li>
            <li>• Körpertemperatur über 40°C</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="alert border-error text-error mt-4 border-2 bg-transparent">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="h-6 w-6 shrink-0 stroke-current"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M10 14l2-2m0 0l2-2m-2 2l-2-2m2 2l2 2m7-2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              >
              </path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs font-bold">Kühlen + sofort zum Tierarzt!</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
